{"tid":580772,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"岩岩收到封email 嚇撚死[yipes]","createTime":"2018-03-04T18:28:39.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-11T06:49:58.000Z","uid":132447,"like":21,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"ad1a7a62f2e2effd36a6811b70d23477bf3ac8ca","tid":580772,"uid":132447,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-04T18:28:39.000Z","msg":"是咁的，小弟本身有一部用左應該有6 年既ipod touch，果陣我入左好撚多歌入部ipod touch 聽當mp3 機咁用，仲有set 左d email account 咁。然後大約 5年前左右轉左用iphone 之後就一直封塵，中間亦因為電腦換過幾部咁本身同部ipod sync ge data 都無晒，但入面有咁多歌就廢事reset 佢，得閒拎返黎當mp3 機出街聽下歌都好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 然後問題就黎了...<br />\n今日我下午食完個飯心血來潮拎返部野出黎插落電腦叉電，諗住過兩日去旅行拎埋去聽歌。叉到一半見到gmail 有個&quot;查看遭拒的登入嘗試&quot;提示，話我個account 俾人入過。咁好正常以為係重開返部機佢自動連返之前入過既email 登入，又入唔到好正常姐，就無理。<br />\n跟住出完街岩岩返黎，再check email 見到有個新郵件, 一check 見到係2014 年我自己寄俾自己，入面無內文而附件係一段幾秒既片。片入面係我岩岩返左屋企，坐係電腦前既片段<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/05/020820_15ca4dc4911c9225dc0cb1e914395555.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F05%2F020820_15ca4dc4911c9225dc0cb1e914395555.png&h=c7ae3af8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n而家起晒雞皮，咁係咪即係我個email account 已經俾人hack 左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申: 段片刪左因為有我樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bdb22628c8699932d814a978394c7813e0ff2568","tid":580772,"uid":38904,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-04T18:32:38.000Z","msg":"其實係部ipod掛住你啫<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f6b2d1c470147c37271d10c498e375382c4195de","tid":580772,"uid":9566,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-04T18:37:25.000Z","msg":"有人入過你屋企偷影你。。"},{"pid":"d9ca2b662bfab4cb99c447a147cd697e37c36b9c","tid":580772,"uid":78429,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-04T18:39:18.000Z","msg":"係因為有你樣先起雞皮啫"},{"pid":"b2baaa60996ca30626f35184b6308dc6254735e9","tid":580772,"uid":157128,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-04T18:41:22.000Z","msg":"睇完三個女人一個因 樓主應該有人格分裂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"792b1d53a51facd5cd77519abf7334cb8d1ec87e","tid":580772,"uid":132447,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bdb22628c8699932d814a978394c7813e0ff2568","tid":580772,"uid":38904,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-04T18:32:38.000Z","msg":"其實係部ipod掛住你啫<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-04T18:42:46.000Z","msg":"咁我都掛住佢既<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/16.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔係都唔會拎返出黎叉電啦"},{"pid":"1c68a5d4d1a8375795953a2ba2ca4f60f3a7ec06","tid":580772,"uid":132447,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f6b2d1c470147c37271d10c498e375382c4195de","tid":580772,"uid":9566,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-04T18:37:25.000Z","msg":"有人入過你屋企偷影你。。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-04T18:43:39.000Z","msg":"而家d hacker會唔會咁重口味玩d恐怖野？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/16.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4de3d6526cece7c9fb1f3ecefb9d574f5968b7b9","tid":580772,"uid":132447,"lik